{"article_id":"deeZEKV3lWCjq35a","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republicans discussed immigration reform at their Thursday retreat .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"House leaders sell immigration plan","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"CAMBRIDGE , Md . -","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"The House Republican leadership is trying to sell their colleagues on a series of broad immigration principles ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"including a path to legal status for those here illegally .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Speaker John Boehner ' s leadership team introduced the principles at their annual policy retreat here .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Top Republicans circulated a tightly held one-page memo","depth":13},{"id":7,"text":"titled \" standards for immigration reform \"","depth":13},{"id":8,"text":"toward the tail-end of a day","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"that include strategy conversations about Obamacare , the economy and the national debt .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"In the private meeting","depth":15},{"id":11,"text":"where the language was introduced ,","depth":15},{"id":12,"text":"Boehner","depth":16},{"id":13,"text":"( R-Ohio )","depth":16},{"id":14,"text":"told Republicans","depth":15},{"id":15,"text":"that the standards are \" as far","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"as we are willing to go . \"","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"\" Nancy Pelosi said yesterday","depth":16},{"id":18,"text":"that for her caucus , it is a special path to citizenship or nothing , \"","depth":16},{"id":19,"text":"Boehner said ,","depth":15},{"id":20,"text":"according to a source in the room .","depth":14},{"id":21,"text":"\" If Democrats insist on that ,","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"then we are not going to get anywhere this year . \"","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"Boehner said","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"the standards represent \" a fair , principled way for us","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"to solve this issue . \"","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"The strategy marks a shift for House Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"In 2013 , Boehner ' s chamber ignored the bipartisan immigration reform bill","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"passed by the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"But toward the end of last year and early this year , Boehner , Majority Leader Eric Cantor","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"( R-Va. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"Whip Kevin McCarthy","depth":15},{"id":32,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":15},{"id":33,"text":"and Rep. Paul Ryan","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"( R-Wis. )","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"began hashing out this approach","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"to rally Republicans toward reform .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"\" It ' s important to act on immigration reform","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"because we ' re focused on jobs and economic growth ,","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"and this is about jobs and growth , \"","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"Boehner said in his pitch in the closed meeting .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"\" Reform is also about our national security .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"The safety and security of our nation depends on our ability","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"to secure our border ,","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"enforce our laws ,","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"improve channels for legal entry to the country ,","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"and identify who is here illegally . \"","depth":16},{"id":47,"text":"Embracing legalization is a modest change for Republican leaders","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"- some of them signaled openness to the idea last year .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"For a Republican Party","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that advocated \" self-deportation \" as recently as 2012 ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"it ' s a massive shift .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Some Republicans fear of the political fallout from immigration reform ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"but the proposal suggests","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"GOP leaders are taking the long view :","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Republicans need to woo the booming Hispanic population","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to stay relevant .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"At the private meeting","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"where the proposal was unveiled ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"lawmakers talked about their distrust","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that President Barack Obama will enforce the law ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"according to sources inside of the room .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Ryan and Boehner spoke in favor of the effort ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"but high-profile conservatives like Rep. Tom Price","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"( R-Ga. )","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and Rep. Jeb Hensarling","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"( R-Texas )","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"were more suspect of the reform push .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" Nobody , even those","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"who want to get this done ,","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"trusts the president , \"","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Rep. Mario Diaz-Balart","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"( R-Fla. )","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"said in a phone interview Thursday evening .","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"\" And I understand it ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"because I don ' t either . \"","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"But legislation on some of the key components of the principles , most notably the legalization part , have not been released","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"and it remains to be seen how the full set of principles are received by rank-and-file House Republicans","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"- many","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who have been skeptical of acting on immigration reform this year .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"The principles stress","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that undocumented immigrants will have to go through the current immigration system","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and complete several prerequisites .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Criminals will not be eligible for legalization .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" These persons could live legally and without fear in the U.S. ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"but only if they were willing to admit their culpability ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"pass rigorous background checks ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"pay significant fines and back taxes ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"develop proficiency in English and American civics ,","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"and be able to support themselves and their families","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"( without access to public benefits ) , \"","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"according to a draft of the document .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"A broad swath of pro-reform groups","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"- from the U.S. Chamber of Commerce to the liberal-leaning America ' s Voice -","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"welcomed the principles .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"But one concern","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"already being raised by Democrats and immigration reform advocates off Capitol Hill","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"is language in the principles","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"that call for \" specific enforcement triggers \" to be in place","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"before undocumented immigrants can get on the legalization track .","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"That section is meant","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"to make sure","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"that the Obama administration","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"- and future presidents -","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"enforce any immigration laws","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"that Congress may pass .","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"One of the most prominent immigration actions from Obama has been halting the deportations of young undocumented immigrants","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"who qualify ,","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"known as Dreamers -","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"a move","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"that was done","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"without the blessing of Congress .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"But Democrats and advocates worry","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"those \" triggers \" will be overly restrictive","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"- preventing millions of undocumented immigrants from beginning the process","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"to become legalized .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"\" It leaves them vulnerable to deportation for God knows how long , \"","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"Kevin Appleby , the director of migration policy for the pro-reform U.S. Conference of Catholic Bishops , said in an e-mail .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Ana Avendaño , the director of immigration and community action for the AFL-CIO , also called the trigger issue a \" serious concern \" for the labor group .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"In a statement , the AFL-CIO called the principles \" flimsy . \"","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"The leadership ' s principles do treat young undocumented immigrants differently , however .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"House Republican leaders declared","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"that lawmakers should give a pathway to legal residence and citizenship for young immigrants","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"who were brought to the United States illegally as children .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"\" For those","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"who meet certain eligiblity standards ,","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"and serve honorably in our military","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"or attain a college degree ,","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"we will do just that , \"","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"the document says .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"The blueprint is also silent","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"on whether the broader undocumented population will ever be able to apply for permanent residency","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"- and eventually , citizenship -","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"by using pathways","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"that currently exist for all immigrants .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"The principles rule out a so-called \" special \" pathway to citizenship","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"- meaning a separate track for undocumented immigrants","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"that isn ' t available to other immigrants .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"The document","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"- drafted by leadership with input from key GOP lawmakers","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"who have been working on immigration -","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"also makes clear","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"that the House will not negotiate with the Senate on its comprehensive bill .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"In fact , GOP leadership has already begun laying out the differences between the House ' s approach and the Senate ' s bill .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"\" The problems in our immigration system must be solved through a step-by-step , common-sense approach","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"that starts with securing our country ' s borders ,","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"enforcing our laws ,","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"and implementing robust enforcement measures , \"","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"the document ' s preamble reads .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"The pathway","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"outlined in the principles","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"does not open up","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"until the nation ' s borders are secure .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Securing America ' s borders has long been a major issue for House Republicans","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"- but how that can actually be accomplished was a major issue","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"in passing the Senate measure .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"The document lays out policies beyond legalization .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"Republicans want to implement a biometric system","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"to track those in the nation on a visa .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"The GOP wants to implement a \" workable electronic employment verification system. \"","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"And the principles also call for an overhaul to the legal immigration system","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"that ' s focused on economic needs , rather than family ties .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"The one-page list of principles has been one of the most hotly anticipated documents in recent memory .","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"Sen. Chuck Schumer","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"( D-N.Y. ) ,","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"one of several key senators","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"who led the immigration reform process in that chamber ,","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"with the House GOP leadership ' s overhaul blueprint , \" the door is open .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"\" While these standards are certainly not everything","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"we would agree with ,","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"they leave a real possibility","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"that Democrats and Republicans , in both the House and Senate , can in some way come together","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"and pass immigration reform","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"that both sides can accept , \"","depth":15},{"id":175,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"Sen. John McCain","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"( R-Ariz. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"another member of the so-called Senate Gang of Eight , praised House Republicans","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"on moving forward on immigration reform","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"by releasing their principles .","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"\" And","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"if","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"[ Speaker John Boehner","depth":17},{"id":184,"text":"( R-Ohio ) ]","depth":17},{"id":185,"text":"hadn ' t gotten control of his conference ,","depth":16},{"id":186,"text":"this wouldn ' t have happened , \"","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"McCain said .","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"\" So maybe there is a silver lining in the shutdown ...","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"I ' ve been digging for that pony for a long time . \"","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"Still , skeptics of a broad immigration reform push were already critical of the House Republican leadership ' s principles .","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"\" In three fundamental respects , the House leaders ' emerging immigration proposal appears to resemble the Senate plan , \"","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"said Sen. Jeff Sessions","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"( R-Ala. ) ,","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"who has been talking with House Republicans on the immigration issue .","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"\" It provides the initial grant of amnesty before enforcement ;","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"it would surge the already unprecedented level of legal lesser-skilled immigration to the U.S.","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"that is reducing wages","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"and increasing unemployment ;","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"and it would offer eventual citizenship to a large number of illegal immigrants and visa overstays . \"","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"Manu Raju contributed to this report .","depth":4},{"id":201,"text":"Seung Min Kim reported from Washington .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":403,"left":203,"right":402,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":203,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":402,"left":2,"right":401,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":401,"left":399,"right":400,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":399,"left":275,"right":398,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":251,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":246,"right":250,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":225,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":204,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elabor